{"tid":702626,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"雨遮互撞掀罵戰！阿叔揮傘狂舞　怒插小巴車窗","createTime":"2018-06-15T05:05:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T07:30:24.000Z","uid":75969,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"89a2895a843d72104eeab8a6f57b74e76acc2963","tid":702626,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T05:05:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180615/photo/bkn-20180615073027201-0615_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180615105828\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180615%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180615073027201-0615_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180615105828&h=d52865e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n夏天為大地帶嚟雨水，更間接牽起雨遮攻防戰？近日網上有片段指，有一對中年男女疑因雨遮問題，與另一名男子展開罵戰，甚至以雨遮作「劍」，瘋狂揮舞，引起網民熱議。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook專頁「全心荃灣」轉載片段，據發貼者指，星期三（13日）中午12點許，有一對中年夫婦經過荃灣河背街時，疑被一扶老攜幼家庭的雨遮撞到。發貼者稱，該夫婦聲言要報警，又用雨遮指嚇該家庭。<br />\n<br />\n從片段可見，該家庭已走上小巴，惟該對中年男女在車外大罵︰「你影乜X嘢呀」、「你唔好X撞到我把遮！」該中年夫婦又不停開合雨遮，用遮在車門中左右狂掃，又以遮把狂篤小巴車窗。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民嘲諷片段有如鬧劇，又笑言「（中年夫婦）係咁打部車，點解司機唔鬧佢」。有網民則認為，「條片冇頭冇尾，拍片嗰個可能都有份撩人」，直斥拍片者「乜都影一餐」。<br />\n<br />\n到底雨遮戰有幾精彩？即刻睇片啦！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180615/bkn-20180615073027201-0615_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180615%2Fbkn-20180615073027201-0615_00822_001.html&d=zojaX6QYh3L6vsaSyb2PlpUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=ea656f2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180615/bkn-20180615073027201-0615_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5e262a300200d68e355d30ac857d832c9ecfdbd","tid":702626,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T05:10:11.000Z","msg":"我唔洗影都影到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e362797d303339988c963e55d04ad618042be79","tid":702626,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T05:34:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0a9ad12295bd9296ea85eef09e2e46e58a12afd6","tid":702626,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T05:35:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b9455d033cc77292bedb4c31555584620e8ba48","tid":702626,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T05:37:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ae4e0dbe5d4a8ccc2c8a8d31759c2c0980e97bab","tid":702626,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T05:37:58.000Z","msg":"吊穿你個西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50b30ebc5f1c616cff9a3a977db02dcb999e8227","tid":702626,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T07:30:24.000Z","msg":"個旁白笑撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}